vote.title: Authorize a three-year master agreement for athletic, physical education, gymnasium supplies, and equipment for the Park and Recreation Department with BSN Sports, LLC in the estimated amount of $500,000 and S&S Worldwide, Inc. in the estimated amount of $350,000 through the Texas Association of School Boards cooperative agreement - Total estimated amount of $850,000 - Financing: General Fund
